OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStill the
OL,6,Fodd shower this evening then becoming
OL,7,Fdry with some good clear spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping tonight. Quite cold with
OL,9,Fperhaps a touch of frost in sheltered
OL,10,Fspots.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA mainly dry day with some
OL,13,Fbright or sunny intervals and variable
OL,14,Fcloud, the best of the the sunshine
OL,15,Faround the coasts. The odd light
OL,16,Fshower possible. A colder day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
