OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry,
OL,6,Fbright start to Sunday, then cloud and
OL,7,Flight rain spreading from northwest.
OL,8,FMonday dry and bright, then some
OL,9,Fpatchy evening rain. Sunny spells and
OL,10,Fa few showers on Tuesday.
